OL,3,CViolent robber posed as wheelchair
OL,4,Cuser before assaulting security guard
OL,6,FA 19 year old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Fthree years and one month after
OL,8,Fviolently assaulting a security guard
OL,9,Fin a Staplehurst supermarket.
OL,11,FOn June 3 2025, Davey Brown pretended
OL,12,Fto be a wheelchair user to hide two
OL,13,Fcrates of beer under a jacket and
OL,14,Fattempted to leave Sainsbury's without
OL,15,Fpaying.
OL,17,FWhen a security guard challenged him,
OL,18,FBrown responded by throwing beer
OL,19,Fbottles and cans, striking the guard,
OL,20,Fand injuring another staff member.
