OL,3,CViolent robber posed as wheelchair
OL,4,Cuser before assaulting security guard
OL,6,FBefore this, the car he was driving
OL,7,Fstruck a stationary vehicle in Four
OL,8,FElms Road, Edenbridge. When the victim
OL,9,Fgot out Brown drove at her before
OL,10,Fspeeding from the scene through a red
OL,11,Flight.
OL,13,FBrown was convicted of robbery,
OL,14,Faffray, criminal damage, common
OL,15,Fassault, threatening behaviour, and
OL,16,Fdriving without insurance. He has also
OL,17,Fbeen banned from driving.
